        <h1>Working At P2</h1>
  </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class='span11 offset1'>
          <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p><strong>P2 Energy Solutions isn’t just a software and technology company.</strong> It’s a place where work, fun, and innovative thinking come together every day. As a member of the P2 team, you’ll work on meaningful projects that positively impact our internal and external customers. Not only do we offer competitive compensation and excellent benefits, but you’ll be challenged, you’ll work with talented people, and you’ll grow both personally and professionally. And most importantly, you’ll have a ton of fun along the way.</p>
</div></div></div>                                      </div>
